  "pages": [
    {
      "text": "Elías was a quiet boy with a big, warm heart.",
      "image": "page-01.webp",
      "bg": "#FFF8E1",
      "accent": "#F9A825",
      "audio": "page-01.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "Every day he walked past an old man sitting outside his school.",
      "image": "page-02.webp",
      "bg": "#FFF3E0",
      "accent": "#FB8C00",
      "audio": "page-02.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "The old man's clothes were worn, and his eyes looked very tired.",
      "image": "page-03.webp",
      "bg": "#FBE9E7",
      "accent": "#E64A19",
      "audio": "page-03.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "One morning, Elías looked down at his lunch and made a quiet choice.",
      "image": "page-04.webp",
      "bg": "#F3E5F5",
      "accent": "#8E24AA",
      "audio": "page-04.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "He set his brown bag softly beside the old man and walked away without a word.",
      "image": "page-05.webp",
      "bg": "#EDE7F6",
      "accent": "#5E35B1",
      "audio": "page-05.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "The old man opened the bag and found rice, beans, and a sweet mango.",
      "image": "page-06.webp",
      "bg": "#E8F5E9",
      "accent": "#43A047",
      "audio": "page-06.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "Tears filled his eyes because someone had cared for him that day.",
      "image": "page-07.webp",
      "bg": "#E0F7FA",
      "accent": "#00838F",
      "audio": "page-07.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "Feeling full of hope, the old man helped a woman whose heavy bags had fallen in the street.",
      "image": "page-08.webp",
      "bg": "#E1F5FE",
      "accent": "#0288D1",
      "audio": "page-08.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "That woman smiled so brightly that she gave her last coin to a little girl selling flowers.",
      "image": "page-09.webp",
      "bg": "#FFF9C4",
      "accent": "#F9A825",
      "audio": "page-09.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "The little girl ran home and surprised her sick mamá with a beautiful yellow bloom.",
      "image": "page-10.webp",
      "bg": "#FCE4EC",
      "accent": "#D81B60",
      "audio": "page-10.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "Her mamá felt so loved that she cooked a big pot of soup and shared it with all her neighbors.",
      "image": "page-11.webp",
      "bg": "#FFF3E0",
      "accent": "#EF6C00",
      "audio": "page-11.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "One of those neighbors was Elías's abuela, who hugged him tight that evening and said, 'God is good.'",
      "image": "page-12.webp",
      "bg": "#F1F8E9",
      "accent": "#558B2F",
      "audio": "page-12.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    },
    {
      "text": "Elías smiled, never knowing his one small act of kindness had wrapped love all around his town.",
      "image": "page-13.webp",
      "bg": "#FFF8E1",
      "accent": "#F9A825",
      "audio": "page-13.mp3",
      "timestamps": []
    }
  ]
}